OL,4,Ctoddlers not wearing seat belts
OL,6,FChildren were among thousands of
OL,7,Fpeople seen not wearing a seat belt by
OL,8,FAI cameras on Devon and Cornwall roads.
OL,10,FThe cameras caught unrestrained
OL,11,Ftoddlers using tablets and children
OL,12,Fsitting on the laps of adults the
OL,13,Ffront passenger seat.
OL,15,FDevon and Cornwall Police said 109
OL,16,Fchildren were among more than 2,000
OL,17,Fdetected by artificial intelligence
OL,18,F(AI) cameras on three A-roads in the
OL,19,Fregion between July and August.
