OL,6,FBetween 25 July and 17 August, the AI
OL,7,Fcameras on the A388 between Saltash
OL,8,Fand Launceston, the A361 between
OL,9,FBarnstaple and Braunton and the A38
OL,10,Fnear Landrake captured 2,239 seat belt
OL,11,Foffences.
OL,13,FMore than 800 mobile phone offences
OL,14,Fwere detected in the same period,
OL,15,Fstatistics from the road safety unit
OL,16,FVision Zero showed.
