OL,6,FHead of Road Safety for Devon and
OL,7,FCornwall Police said he hopes the
OL,8,Ftechnology "will help send a clear
OL,9,Fmessage to the small minority of
OL,10,Fmotorists who continue to flout the
OL,11,Flaw".
OL,13,F"We continue to see serious and fatal
OL,14,Fcollisions involving people who were
OL,15,Fnot wearing seatbelts.
OL,17,F"There is also a problem with mobile
OL,18,Fphone use behind the wheel, which is
OL,19,Fboth dangerous and illegal.
