OL,6,F"While we know the majority of drivers
OL,7,Fin Devon and Cornwall are safe,
OL,8,Frespectful and conscientious
OL,9,Fmotorists, sadly there is a minority
OL,10,Fwho are still putting people's lives
OL,11,Fat risk.
OL,13,F"We are employing this new technology
OL,14,Fto send a clear message to anyone who
OL,15,Fcontinues to use their phone behind
OL,16,Fthe wheel ` you will get caught."
